name: RBC Target 2031 U.S. Corporate Bond ETF
longDescription: To achieve the funds objectives, by investing primarily in a portfolio of investment grade fixed-income securities issued in the U.S. market by U.S. and foreign corporations that mature in the same calendar year as RBC Target 2031 U.S. Corporate Bond ETFs Termination Date. RBC Target 2031 U.S. Corporate Bond ETF will terminate on its Termination Date. The investment objective of RBC Target 231 U.S. Corporate Bond ETF is to provide income, for a limited period of time ending on RBC Target 231 U.S. Corporate Bond ETFs Termination Date.
